oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tribute - The Life and Music of Dobro master Josh Graves - 2013-04-20
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tribute to the Life and Music of Dobro master Burkett H. ("Uncle Josh") Graves from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on April 20, 2013. Participants include Fred Bartenstein and Tim Graves.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Hosted by Fred Bartenstein and Tim Graves. Includes questions from the audience. Performances include; Demonstration Of Great Speckled Bird Style (Tim Brooks); Demonstration Of Blues Style (Tim Brooks); Demonstration Of Three Finger Style (Tim Brooks); recorded audio excerpts; It Wasn't God Who Made Honky Tonk Angels (Tim Brooks); Reading of Fire On The Bus Story (Fred Bartenstein);
